sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant User
  participant ProdApp as PROD App
  participant ProdBackend as PROD Backend
  participant Slash as Slash Handoff Mode
  participant Queue as Control Plane Queue
  participant DevWorker as DEV Worker
  participant Stage as DEV Stage Worktree
  participant DevChat as DEV Spec Chat

  User->>ProdApp: Work normally in PROD
  ProdApp->>ProdBackend: Chat/run real work
  Note over ProdBackend: Normal PROD has no DEV/backlog context
  User->>ProdApp: Invoke /dev-plan slash/action
  ProdApp->>Slash: Load temporary handoff context
  Slash->>ProdBackend: Submit handoff payload
  ProdBackend->>Queue: enqueue_only immutable item
  Queue-->>ProdBackend: item_id + queued status
  ProdBackend-->>ProdApp: Confirmation only
  Queue->>DevWorker: Claimed by DEV worker
  DevWorker->>Stage: Materialize or attach spec in DEV worktree
  DevWorker->>DevChat: Bind chat to stage/spec/branch
  DevChat-->>User: DEV shows stage-specific work
